description: Non-Material ammendment to planning permission 16/AP/2740 'Demolition of existing ward buildings and nurses accommodation and development of site to provide a new secondary school within the retained and refurbished 'Chateau' building fronting East Dulwich Grove and in a series of new buildings and extensions up to 5 storeys high,comprising teaching and administration spaces, dining and indoor sports hall, multi-use games area, accesses, car parking and servicing areas and landscaping (Use Class D1)' comprising general internal reconfiguration of buildings, retention and reuse of existing mezzanine level in 'Chateau' building, reduction in height of new building from two to one storey and associated amendments to building elevations.
